Commissioner%2C%20and%20Alvin%20Bragg%2C%20Manhattan%20DA%2C%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20announcing%20indictment%20of%20Mangione.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761e5421d90e3bcf31d706f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELaura%20Italiano%20%2F%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2276e4f4ca-3312-42a4-9eef-9bba88879bc6%5C%22%3ELaw%2C%20order%2C%20and%20victims%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20sentencings%2C%20Carro%20is%20an%20emphatic%20advocate%20for%20law%2C%20order%2C%20and%20victims%2C%20his%20many%20news%20clippings%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20only%20imagine%20what%20memories%20are%20haunting%20the%20victim%20in%20this%20case%20and%20his%20significant%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20last%20year%20at%20a%20recent%20high-profile%20sentencing%2C%20for%20the%20random%2C%20attempted%20slashing%20murder%20of%20a%20French%20tourist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20Carro%20presided%20over%20the%20trial%20of%20an%20NYPD%20officer%20accused%20of%20raping%20a%20young%20fashion%20executive%20%E2%80%94%20a%20woman%20he'd%20been%20dispatched%20to%20help%20when%20she%20was%20too%20intoxicated%20to%20get%20out%20of%20her%20taxi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20jury%20cleared%20the%20officer%20of%20rape%20and%20convicted%20him%20of%20official%20misconduct%20for%20the%20three%20caught-on-video%20visits%20he%20made%20to%20the%20woman's%20apartment%20during%20his%20shift%20that%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20misconduct%20offenses%20%26quot%3Brip%20at%20that%20fabric%20that%20holds%20us%20all%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Carro%20told%20the%20former%20officer%2C%20Kenneth%20Moreno%2C%20before%20sentencing%20him%20to%20a%20year%20at%20Rikers%20Island%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%2C%20sir%2C%20ripped%20a%20gaping%20hole%20in%20that%20fabric%20in%20committing%20those%20crimes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Carro's%20biggest%20media%20case%20until%20now