ld%2C%20how%20are%20you%2C%20as%20a%20non-technical%20person%2C%20going%20to%20call%20my%20BS%20on%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20Lerer%2C%20managing%20partner%20at%20Lerer%20Hippeau%2C%20says%20he%20wants%20to%20hire%20%26quot%3Byounger%20people%20who%20are%20more%20natively%20growing%20up%20with%20AI%20and%20think%20about%20AI%20as%20less%20of%20a%20novelty%20and%20more%20of%20just%20a%20sort%20of%20inevitability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a770fe7-c92e-4f03-922f-8c2eeeeaf299%5C%22%3EHiring%20for%20the%20investing%20theme%20du%20jour%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Suster%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Upfront%20Ventures%2C%20says%20he%20used%20to%20recruit%20from%20blue-chip%20consulting%20firms%20like%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20and%20Bain%20%26amp%3B%20Company%2C%20whereas%20recent%20hires%20have%20all%20brought%20specific%20expertise%20in%20areas%20the%20firm%20wants%20to%20focus%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20generalist%20works%20anymore%20because%20venture%20capital%20is%20too%20competitive%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Suster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20much%20deeper%20in%20our%20industries%2C%20and%20so%20when%20we%20went%20to%20invest%20in%20healthcare%2C%20we%20hired%20a%20healthcare%20expert.%20Now%20that%20we're%20doing%20more%20semiconductors%2C%20we're%20trying%20to%20get%20somebody%20with%20semiconductor%20experience.%20We're%20doing%20more%20with%20satellites%2C%20so%20we%20want%20someone%20from%20day%20one%20who%20understands%20the%20customer%20and%20the%20technology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpfront%20is%20currently%20hiring%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fupfrontvc.notion.site%2FInvestment-Associate-Data-ML-12d841cdc6a8800b988cc35cfa850172%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20investment%20associate%20focused%20on%20machine%20learning%20and%20AI.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Khosla%20Ventures%20hired%20John%20Chu%20as%20a%20partner%2C%20who%20held%20senior%20engineering%20roles%20at%20Meta%20and%20Opendoor.%20This%20fall%2C%20Katie%20Jacobs%20Stanton%2C%20a%20longtime%20Twitter%20insider%20turned%20venture%20capitalist%2C%20hired%20a%20former%20engineering%20leader%20to%20her%20firm%2C%20Moxxie%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAshwin%20Lalendran%20worked%20on%20drones%20at%20the%20Air%20Force%20Research%20Laboratory%2C%20shipped%203D%20vision%20software%20for%20Apple's%20mapping%20and%20self-driving-car%20projects%2C%20and%20led%20a%20team%20of%20engineers%20to%20scale%20the%20world's%20largest%20private-owned%20network%20of%20ocean%20sensors%20at%20Sofar%20Ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20joins%20Moxxie's%20deep%20bench%20of%20operators%20to%20assist%20with%20sourcing%2C%20evaluating%2C%20and%20closing%20deals%20in%20deep%20tech%2C%20hardware%2C%20and%20national%20security%2C%20areas%20where%20Moxxie%20has%20deepened%20its%20focus%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirms%20have%20long%20hired%20from%20certain%20networks%20based%20on%20the%20investment%20theme%20du%20jour%2C%20according%20to%20Yoni%20Rechtman%2C%20a%20principal%20at%20Slow%20Ventures%2C%20an%20early%20investor%20in%20Robinhood%20and%20PillPack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20fintech%20boom%2C%20Stripe%20was%20the%20hot%20ticket%2C%20and%20investors%20rushed%20to%20hire%20from%20the%20fintech%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20firms%20are%20chasing%20after%20ex-Palantir%20and%20OpenAI%20employees%20to%20fill%20out%20their%20ranks%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20them%20are%20restaffing%20after%20years%20of%20hiring%20slowdowns%20or%20job%20cuts%2C%20though%20such%20moves%20remain%20rare%20in%20the%20venture%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20add%20expertise%20and%20networks%20in%20their%20fields%20of%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlow%20Ventures%20is%20looking%20to%20add%20as%20many%20as%20four%20associates%20over%20the%20next%20year%20based%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20talent%20on%20the%20market%2C%20Rechtman%20said.%20Being%20technical%20as%20an%20associate%20is%20a%20plus%20but%20not%20a%20requirement%2C%20though.%20%26quot%3BBeing%20credible%20with%20founders%20because%20you%20worked%20at%20OpenAI%20is%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20Rechtman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20much%20for%20your%20ability%20to%20pick%20stocks%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cccd1db9-fa87-4de6-acbc-1dd5b989a4b8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EVC%20firms%20can't%20compete%20with%20startups%20on%20compensation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIncreasingly%2C%20venture%20firms%20find%20themselves%20squaring%20off%20with%20the%20hottest%20AI%20companies%20to%20secure%20top%20talent%2C%20according%20to%20Dan%20Miller%2C%20a%20recruiter%20and%20partner%20at%20True%20Search.%20%26quot%3BFor%20a%20lot%20of%20VC%20firms%2C%20the%20stiffest%20competition%20for%20talent%20over%20the%20last%20year%20has%20been%20OpenAI%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Miller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20worked%20with%20several%20venture%20firms%20on%20partner%20and%20principal%20searches%20that%20lost%20candidates%20to%20the%20ChatGPT-maker.%20That%20is%20largely%20because%20OpenAI%20offers%20salaries%20above%20market%20rate%20and%20a%20chance%20to%20contribute%20to%20cutting-edge%20research%20and%20development.%20Those%20candidates%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20gain%20experience%20that%20opens%20doors%20to%20top-tier%20venture%20firms%20down%20the%20line%2C%20Miller%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20salary%20for%20a%20VC%20with%201-3%20years%20of%20experience%20is%20%24264%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20Glassdoor%2C%20an%20anonymous%20job%20review%20site.%20By%20contrast%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-money-openai-employees-make-compensation-elon-musk-lawsuit-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20median%20yearly%20total%20compensation%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20%24534%2C197%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FLevels.fyi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELevels.fyi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20tracks%20compensation%20data%20at%20tech%20firms%20and%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20VC%20will%20pay%20what%20a%20good%20AI%20engineer%20can%20make%20a%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20M13's%20Hoffman.%20%26quot%3BSo%20our%20job%20is%20to%20find%20people%20who%20get%20excited%20about%20working%20in%20venture%20and%20helping%20to%20build%20a%20number%20of%20companies%20rather%20than%20just%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDas%20said%20he%20did%20take%20a%20step%20down%20in%20pay%20when%20he%20joined%20Menlo%20Ventures%20after%20Glean%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20wasn't%20concerned%20because%20if%20this%20worked%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20long-term%20bet%20where%20the%20comp%20would%20be%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20Das%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20that%20he%20was%20excited%20to%20try%20venture%20because%20he%20was%20ready%20for%20a%20new%20challenge%20and%20also%20thought%20his%20technical%20chops%20would%20give%20him%20an%20edge%20over%20generalist%20investors%20evaluating%20AI%20infrastructure%20and%20machine%20learning%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20a%20lot%20of%20venture%20capitalists%20were%20actually%20pretty%20terrible%20doing%20diligence%20on%20companies%20that%20were%20technical%20because%20they%20weren't%20technical.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDas%20was%20recently%20on%20a%20call%20with%20co-investors%2C%20and%20they%20needed%20his%20expertise.%20They%20were%20stumped%20and%20needed%20help%20understanding%20some%20of%20the%20jargon%20the%20founder%20of%20an%20AI%20startup%20was%20using.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20chuckled%20because%20every%20second%20pitch%20I%20see%20is%20some%20version%20of%20fancy%20technical%20lingo%2C%20which%20actually%20doesn't%20mean%20much%20if%20you%20dig%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Das%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20something%20a%20traditional%20investor%20has%20a%20really%20hard%20time%20seeing%20through.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2