other%20startups%20can%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20near-term%20outlook%20for%20M%26amp%3BA%20activity%20has%20gotten%20brighter%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterest-rate-decision-this-week-federal-reserve-inflation-job-market-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20interest%20rates%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereducing%20the%20cost%20of%20borrowing.%20Wall%20Street%20execs%20are%20optimistic%20that%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20and%20any%20business-friendly%20regulations%20that%20may%20come%20with%20it%2C%20will%20be%20a%20tailwind%20for%20dealmaking.%20Also%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-down-rounds-rise-valuations-investors-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompanies%20resetting%20their%20valuations%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20spur%20more%20transactions%20to%20close%20as%20price%20expectations%20align%20between%20buyers%20and%20sellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%3Cspan%3E%2C%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-could-help-deregulate-tech-amid-a-trump-victory-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVCs%20and%20founders%20are%20hopeful%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0about%20the%20anticipated%20looser%20environment%2C%20which%20could%20boost%20tech%20building%20and%20dealmaking.%20VCs%2C%20which%20rely%20on%20selling%20startups%20in%20M%26amp%3BA%20deals%20for%20many%20of%20their%20returns%2C%20have%20been%20dampened%20by%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-vcs-in-silicon-valley-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20Trade%20Commission's%20antitrust%20stance%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20M%26amp%3BA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELouisa%20AI%20was%20built%20to%20suggest%20potential%20deals%20based%20on%20the%20data%20it's%20exposed%20to.%20It%20ingests%20information%20about%20who%20and%20what%20employees%20know%20by%20plugging%20into%20company%20CRMs%2C%20messaging%20platforms%20like%20Slack%20and%20Symphony%2C%20and%20email%20providers.%20Since%20spinning%20out%20of%20Goldman%20Sachs%20in%202023%2C%20Louisa%20AI%20has%20raised%20%245%20million%20in%20seed%20funding.%20It%20suggests%20about%20%241%20billion%20in%20deal%20values%20per%20quarter%2C%20Doctor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20highlights%20mutual%20connections%20to%20establish%20a%20warm%20introduction%2C%20which%20can%20make%20all%20the%20difference%20in%20the%20multi-billion%20investment%20banking%20industry%20built%20on%20relationships.%20While%20running%20the%20bank-solutions%20group%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20Rohan%20Doctor%20used%20his%20network%20to%20close%20transactions%20worth%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars.%20As%20a%20startup%20founder%2C%20it's%20been%20a%20different%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20tried%20the%20cold%20outreach%20and%20just%20emailing%2C%26quot%3B%20Doctor%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20startup%20stopped%20doing%20that%20after%20it%20didn't%20yield%20good%20results.%20What%20has%20worked%20for%20Doctor%20is%20realizing%20he%20knows%20someone%20who%20knows%20someone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELouisa%20AI%20scored%20the%20chipmaker%20contract%20after%20the%20AI%20flagged%20that%20one%20of%20Doctor's%20staff%20used%20to%20work%20for%20someone%20who%20now%20worked%20at%20the%20chip%20manufacturer.%20With%20the%20consultancy%2C%20one%20of%20Louisa%20AI's%20investors%20connected%20Doctor%20with%20the%20consulting%20firm%20they%20used%20to%20work%20for.%20He%20declined%20to%20name%20these%20firms%20due%20to%20non-disclosure%20agreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20needs%20to%20be%20warm%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20big%20companies%20doing%20big%20things%20with%20other%20people.%20It%20has%20to%20rely%20on%20trust%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.