Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americangaming.org%2Fresources%2Famerican-attitudes-towards-gaming-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Gaming%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2055%25%20of%20surveyed%20adults%20said%20they%20had%20participated%20in%20some%20sort%20of%20gambling%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americangaming.org%2Fresources%2Famerican-attitudes-2023%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eup%20from%2049%25%20in%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Americans%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wshu.org%2Fconnecticut-news%2F2024-09-16%2Fct-online-sports-betting-gambling-addiction%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eare%20expected%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20wager%20some%20%24150%20billion%20on%20sports%20this%20year%2C%20up%20from%20about%20%24120%20billion%20in%202023.%20People%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolymarket-kalshi-trump-victory-future-prediction-markets-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebet%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%202024%20election%2C%20with%20companies%20such%20as%20Polymarket%20and%20Kalshi%20raking%20in%20big%20bucks.%20The%20trading%20platform%20Robinhood%20got%20into%20presidential-election%20betting%2C%20and%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Frobinhood-ceo-says-keenly-looking-into-sports-betting-space-1034098875%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esays%20it's%20looking%20into%3C%2Fa%3E%20sports%20gambling%20now%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20explicit%20betting%2C%20either.%20A%20lot%20of%20%26quot%3Binvesting%26quot%3B%20looks%20very%20much%20like%20gambling%20nowadays.%20There's%20an%20increasing%20acknowledgment%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-all-time-high-etfs-crypto-price-crash-boom-bust-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoint%20of%20bitcoin%20is%20really%20%26quot%3Bnumber%20go%20up%26quot%3B%20(and%20down)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20it's%20a%20speculative%20investment%20without%20much%20of%20a%20use%20case.%20Small-time%20investors%20doing%20options%20trading%20on%20platforms%20such%20as%20Robinhood%20aren't%20banking%20on%20a%20stock's%20underlying%20value%3B%20they're%20just%20guessing%20at%20where%20it's%20headed%20over%20the%20next%20little%20while.%20And%20the%20meme%20coins%20are%20just%20complete%20casinolike%20chaos%2C%20full%20of%20pump%20and%20dumps%20and%20rug%20pulls%20and%20meteoric%20rises%20and%20falls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20you're%20not%20putting%20money%20on%20the%20line%2C%20it's%20almost%20impossible%20to%20escape%20the%20proliferation%20of%20gambling.%20There%20are%20unceasing%20commercials%20during%20sports%20games%20and%20a%20deluge%20of%20ads%20on%20our%20phones.%20Culturally%2C%20the%20broader%20acceptance%20of%20gambling%20is%20on%20the%20upswing%20%E2%80%94%20betting's%20positioned%20as%20cool%20and%20exciting%20and%20fun.%20There's%20not%20so%20much%20focus%20on%20the%20downsides%20yet.%20Betting%20is%20in%20its%20Marlboro%20Man%20era%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20dealt%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20definitely%20a%20younger%20cohort%20that%20is%20trying%20to%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20say%20get%20rich%20fast%2C%20but%20they're%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20get%20around%20the%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Chad%20Beynon%2C%20an%20equity%20analyst%20at%20Macquarie%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20can%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20formats%20%E2%80%94%20betting%20on%20a%20football%20game%20or%20piling%20into%20a%20meme%20coin%20because%20some%20guy%20on%20X%20said%20it%20was%20the%20next%20big%20thing.%20It%20sounds%20more%20appealing%2C%20though%20not%20more%20realistic%2C%20than%20a%20traditional%209-to-5%20job.%20That's%20especially%20pertinent%20in%20an%20economy%20where%20people%20don't%20feel%20particularly%20optimistic%20about%20their%20prospects.%20Instead%20of%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibecession-when-will-the-economy-get-better-inflation-recession-trump-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evibecession%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20maybe%20what's%20happening%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bvibe-screw-it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20novel%20%E2%80%94%20and%20notable%20%E2%80%94%20gambling%20story%20in%20the%20US%20remains%20the%20explosion%20of%20sports%20betting.%20Since%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202018%20struck%20down%20a%20federal%20law%20prohibiting%20it%2C%2038%20states%20plus%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20have%20legalized%20wagering%20on%20games.%20The%20past%20few%20years%20have%20been%20a%20land%20grab%20of%20sorts%2C%20with%20companies%20such%20as%20DraftKings%2C%20FanDuel%2C%20Caesars%2C%20MGM%2C%20and%20even%20Disney%20(via%20ESPN)%20trying%20to%20get%20a%20piece%20of%20what%20they%20hope%20will%20be%20a%20very%20lucrative%20pie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20one%20that%20opened%20the%20floodgates%20in%20terms%20of%20creating%20a%20large%20addressable%20market%20and%20throwing%20a%20spotlight%20on%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20US%20online-gambling%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Grove%2C%20a%20sports-gambling-industry%20investor%20at%20Acies%20Investments%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20two%20operators%20%E2%80%94%20DraftKings%20and%20FanDuel%20%E2%80%94%20have%20managed%20to%20amass%20a%20lot%20of%20market%20share%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-betting-apps-online-gambling-lottery-draftkings-fanduel-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estart%20to%20venture%20into%20other%20arenas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20lotteries%20and%20iGaming%2C%20the%20industry%20term%20for%20online%20blackjack%2C%20roulette%2C%20and%20slot%20machines%2C%20which%20is%20thus%20far%20legal%20in%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20states.%20Adjacent%20products%20around%20daily%20fantasy%20sports%2C%20such%20as%20PrizePicks%2C%20have%20taken%20hold%20as%20well.%20It%20%26quot%3Bjust%20shows%20that%20consumers%20are%20clamoring%20for%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20Grove%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20still%20room%20for%20growth%20in%20sports%20betting%2C%20though%20it's%20increasingly%20limited.%20There%20are%20some%20big%20holdout%20markets%2C%20such%20as%20Texas%20and%20California%2C%20and%20only%20about%20one-fifth%20of%20the%20population%20has%20bet%20on%20a%20sport%20in%20the%20past%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20AGA.%20But%20the%20holdout%20states%20are%20holding%20out%20for%20a%20reason%2C%20and%20at%20least%20some%20aren't%20likely%20to%20change%20course.%20Companies%20sort%20of%20have%20to%20look%20elsewhere%20to%20get%20people%20to%20open%20their%20wallets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20business%20model%20to%20work%2C%20you%20probably%20need%20to%20cross-sell%20to%20other%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20Beynon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20takeoff%20of%20sports%20gambling%20has%20many%20businesses%20looking%20around%20and%20wondering%20just%20what%20else%20people%20are%20willing%20to%20bet%20on%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20guessing%20correctly%20that%20the%20list%20of%20possibilities%20is%20long.%20Maybe%20sports%20betting%20isn't%20for%20you.%20That's%20fine%2C%20but%20what%20about%20an%20online%20lottery%3F%20Or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bettorsinsider.com%2Fcasino%2F2024%2F06%2F25%2Fwhat-are-sweepstakes-casinos-and-how-do-they-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esweepstakes%20casinos%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Or%20a%20slot%20machine%20on%20your%20phone%3F%20Or%20the%20next%20Treasury%20secretary%20of%20the%20United%20States%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20minute%20that%20you%20got%20widespread%20regulated%20online%20gambling%20in%20the%20US%2C%20it%20was%20inevitable%20that%20nontraditional%20stakeholders%20were%20going%20to%20look%20at%20getting%20in%20on%20the%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20Grove%20said.%20%26quot%3BRobinhood%20is%20one%20example%20of%20that%2C%20and%20prediction%20markets%20are%20one%20of%20the%20most%20likely%20vectors%20for%20that%20expansion%2C%20but%20they're%20far%20from%20the%20only%20brand%20or%20the%20only%20vector%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20see%20explore%20online%20gambling%20in%20years%20ahead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20sports%20betting%2C%202024%20was%20a%20monumental%20year%20for%20prediction%20markets%20and%20crypto.%20People%20spent%20millions%20of%20dollars%20betting%20on%20the%20election%2C%20despite%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Ffbi-reportedly-raids-polymarket-ceos-home-1034011437%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegal%20gray%20area%20around%20political%20gambling%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20Polymarket%2C%20players%20%E2%80%94%20though%20not%20Americans%20%E2%80%94%20can%20bet%20whether%20the%20US%20will%20confirm%20aliens%20exist%20or%20if%20Luigi%20Mangione%2C%20the%20suspect%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20UnitedHealthcare's%20CEO%2C%20will%20plead%20guilty.%20In%20Cryptoland%2C%20bitcoin%20surpassed%20the%20%24100%2C000%20mark%2C%20and%20despite%20constant%20scams%2C%20the%20meme-coin%20market%20is%20as%20alive%20as%20ever.%20These%20are%20not%20legitimate%20investments%3B%20they're%20bets%20people%20are%20making%20that%20they%20can%20get%20out%20before%20everyone%20else.%20(Sometimes%2C%20in%20the%20pump%20and%20dump%2C%20you%20think%20you're%20the%20dumper%20when%20you're%20really%20the%20dumpee.)%20Given%20Donald%20Trump's%20election%2C%20it%20doesn't%20look%20like%20tough%20regulation%20is%20coming%20for%20the%20crypto%20space%20anytime%20soon%2C%20so%20hold%20on%20to%20your%20hats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBroadly%2C%20gambling%20has%20been%20normalized%20across%20American%20culture.%20Sports%20leagues%20used%20to%20be%20anxious%20about%20sports%20betting%20and%20worry%20it%20would%20turn%20off%20fans.%20Now%20they've%20seen%20the%20dollar%20signs%20and%20embraced%20it.%20The%20vibe%20around%20elections%20betting%20is%20that%20it's%20kind%20of%20cool%20and%20smart%2C%20a%20wisdom-of-the-crowds%20way%20to%20prove%20your%20political%20chops.%20With%20crypto%2C%20the%20hope%20is%20everybody's%20going%20to%20get%20their%20bag%20sooner%20or%20later%2C%20or%20if%20not%2C%20at%20least%20they%20think%20they're%20in%20on%20the%20joke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20consumer%20has%20different%20motivations%20for%20why%20they're%20doing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Steve%20Ruddock%2C%20a%20gambling-industry%20analyst%20and%20consultant%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstraighttothepoint.substack.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStraight%20to%20the%20Point%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20newsletter%20about%20gambling.%20%26quot%3BSome%20are%20doing%20it%20purely%20for%20entertainment.%20Some%20are%20doing%20it%20as%20a%20time%20sink.%20Some%20small%20percentage%20are%20doing%20it%20because%20they're%20addicted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20easy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20responsible%20%E2%80%94%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20harms%20of%20gambling%20culture.%20There's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-betting-debt-bankruptcy-gambling-young-men-research-addiction-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevidence%20to%20suggest%3C%2Fa%3E%20sports%20betting%20in%20the%20US%20is%20getting%20people%20into%20trouble%20with%20debt%20collectors%2C%20leading%20to%20missed%20car%20payments%2C%20and%20may%20even%20cause%20a%20spike%20in%20bankruptcies.%20When%20people%20are%20betting%20on%20a%20baseball%20game%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsight.kellogg.northwestern.edu%2Farticle%2Fonline-sports-betting-is-draining-household-savings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey're%20not%20putting%20money%20into%20long-term%20investments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20households%20that%20are%20already%20under%20financial%20strain%20are%20harder%20hit.%20And%20whatever%20negative%20impacts%20occur%20aren't%20limited%20to%20gamblers%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20harms%20radiate%20out%20into%20families%2C%20into%20the%20economy%2C%20into%20many%20sectors%20of%20social%20and%20cultural%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rachel%20Volberg%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Massachusetts%20Amherst%20who%20researches%20gambling.%20Most%20research%20suggests%20about%201%25%20of%20adults%20develop%20a%20gambling%20disorder.%20But%20just%20because%20you%20don't%20meet%20the%20clinical%20criteria%20for%20a%20disorder%20doesn't%20mean%20all%20is%20fine%20and%20dandy%2C%20Volberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BTo%20only%20talk%20about%20the%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg%20means%20you%20miss%2090%25%20of%20the%20impacts%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGambling%20companies%20have%20mechanisms%20in%20place%20to%20ensure%20responsible%20gambling.%20(Not%20to%20mention%20that%20some%20companies%20offering%20crypto%20and%20high-flying%20stock%20trading%20say%20this%20is%20not%20gambling%20at%20all.)%20Reasonable%20minds%20can%20question%20how%20effective%20those%20are.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20impetus%20placed%20on%20individual%20gamblers%20to%20police%20themselves%20and%20set%20their%20own%20limits%2C%20and%20even%20if%20you%20do%20reach%20your%20limit%2C%20you%20can%20move%20on%20to%20another%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sudden%20boom%20has%20pushed%20public%20health%20experts%20in%20the%20US%20and%20worldwide%20to%20sound%20the%20alarm%20on%20gambling.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flanpub%2Farticle%2FPIIS2468-2667(24)00248-2%2Ffulltext%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20The%20Lancet%20Public%20Health%20commission%20on%20gambling%20found%20that%20nearly%20450%20million%20people%20around%20the%20globe%20have%20experienced%20at%20least%20one%20behavioral%20symptom%20or%20negative%20consequence%20from%20gambling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20answer%2C%20globally%2C%20that%20the%20commission%20puts%20forth%20is%2C%20'Come%20on%2C%20guys%2C%20wake%20up%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Malcolm%20Sparrow%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20the%20practice%20of%20public%20management%20at%20Harvard%20and%20one%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20commission.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20a%20very%20rapid%20growth%20period.%20The%20assumption%20is%20that%20legalization%2C%20which%20is%20already%20running%20a%20pace%2C%20is%20going%20to%20just%20continue%20until%20it's%20ubiquitous.%20And%20we%20are%20not%20paying%20enough%20attention%20to%20gambling-related%20harms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20the%20thing%2C%20though%3A%20Gambling%20is%20fun.%20Generally%2C%20people%20do%20have%20a%20right%20to%20use%20their%20money%20how%20they%20please%2C%20and%20most%20can%20gamble%20responsibly.%20Exactly%20how%20to%20regulate%20and%20where%20to%20draw%20lines%20is%20complicated%2C%20whether%20you're%20talking%20about%20an%20in-game%20bet%20or%20an%20obscure%20penny%20stock%20or%20a%20meme%20coin%20that%20makes%20zero%20sense.%20But%20public%20health%20experts%20say%20it's%20important%20to%20figure%20out%20where%20to%20draw%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20many%20other%20public%20health%20issues%2C%20we%20are%2C%20to%20a%20degree%2C%20paternalistic%2C%26quot%3B%20Sparrow%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20must%20wear%20a%20seatbelt.%20We%20don't%20sell%20alcohol%20to%20kids.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20weird%20thing%20about%20the%20current%20moment%20is%20once%20you%20start%20to%20notice%20the%20prevalence%20of%20gambling%20in%20a%20few%20places%2C%20you%20start%20to%20see%20it%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94%20I%20see%20it%20in%20my%20own%20life.%20I%20was%20at%20a%20New%20York%20Rangers%20game%20the%20other%20weekend%2C%20and%20not%20one%20but%20two%20betting%20apps%20were%20advertising%20on%20the%20ice.%20On%20a%20recent%20trip%20to%20New%20Jersey%2C%20I%20took%20advantage%20of%20an%20online%20casino%2C%20which%20is%20legal%20in%20the%20state.%20I%20lost%20%2410%20on%20blackjack%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes.%20Beyond%20sports%2C%20many%20of%20my%20friends%20and%20family%20are%20at%20least%20dabbling%20in%20crypto%20and%20have%20taken%20note%20of%20prediction%20markets.%20One%20group%20I%20know%20is%20talking%20about%20organizing%20a%20party-bus%20trip%20to%20Atlantic%20City%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20just%20because.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20not%20to%20wonder%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20culture%20now%20that%20gambling%20has%20gone%20from%20a%20no-no%20to%20out%20in%20the%20open%20and%20even%20hip.%20What's%20getting%20its%20claws%20in%20us%2C%20and%20why%20is%20it%20working%20right%20now%20in%20particular%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENatasha%20Sch%C3%BCll%2C%20a%20cultural%20anthropologist%20at%20New%20York%20University%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BAddiction%20by%20Design%3A%20Machine%20Gambling%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20me%20she'd%20identified%20four%20shared%20criteria%20of%20products%20that%20hook%20and%20hold%20us%2C%20from%20betting%20apps%20to%20dating%20apps%2C%20which%20are%20a%20little%20bit%20like%20gambling.%20They're%20antisocial%20and%20solitary%2C%20so%20you%20can%20get%20lost%20in%20your%20own%20flow.%20They%20offer%20continuous%2C%20fast%20feedback%2C%20which%20serves%20as%20reinforcement.%20They're%20unpredictable%2C%20so%20you%20can't%20be%20exactly%20sure%20when%20a%20reward%20will%20come.%20And%20they%20never%20come%20to%20a%20close%20or%20resolve%20%E2%80%94%20you%20just%20keep%20going.%20The%20result%20is%20that%20people%20get%20pulled%20into%20what%20she%20describes%20as%20a%20gambling%20%26quot%3Bmachine%20zone%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20the%20world%20sort%20of%20falls%20away%2C%20and%20people%20fall%20into%20a%20rhythm%20of%20go%2C%20then%20again%2C%20then%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20certainly%20is%20a%20cultural%20story%20to%20tell%20here%20too%2C%20where%20we're%20living%20in%20a%20context%20of%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20world%2C%20whether%20politically%20or%20environmental%20or%20economic%20uncertainty%2C%26quot%3B%20Sch%C3%BCll%20said.%20When%20you%20gamble%2C%20you're%20diving%20into%20uncertainty%20and%20chance%2C%20but%20also%20in%20an%20ordered%2C%20calm%2C%20digital%20environment%20that's%20cordoned%20off%20from%20the%20outside%20world.%20%26quot%3BIt%20might%20start%20being%20about%20thrill%20and%20suspense%20and%20imagining%20a%20big%20win%20or%20imagining%20that%20you're%20having%20an%20encounter%20with%20chance%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20once%20you%20put%20yourself%20in%20the%20seat%2C%20so%20to%20speak%2C%20and%20start%20having%20the%20interaction%2C%20the%20formatting%20of%20it%20and%20the%20flow%20of%20it%20gives%20you%20this%20other%20thing.%20It%20gives%20you%20this%20way%20to%20modulate%20your%20affect%20and%20go%20into%20a%20zone%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20avoid%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20be%20the%20case%20that%20in%2010%20years%2C%20we'll%20look%20back%20at%20the%20current%20moment%20and%20realize%20this%20was%20all%20fine%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20OK%20that%20people%20were%20gambling%20a%20bunch%2C%20that%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshohei-ohtani-interpreter-ippei-mizuhara-charged-sports-betting-court-documents-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emajor%20athletes%20were%20getting%20caught%20up%20in%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hey%2C%20maybe%20even%20the%20meme-coin%20stuff%20will%20work%20out.%20The%20likelier%20scenario%20is%20that%20we%20wonder%20what%20we%20were%20even%20doing.%20Or%20we%20realize%20we%20probably%20should've%20done%20things%20a%20little%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVolberg%2C%20from%20UMass%20Amherst%2C%20has%20been%20studying%20gambling%20for%2040%20years%20and%20has%20seen%20this%20story%20play%20out%20before%20in%20other%20countries.%20Some%20form%20of%20gambling%20gets%20the%20go-ahead%2C%20it%20takes%20off%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20lag%20in%20realizing%20the%20consequences%20and%20getting%20guardrails%20in%20place%20appropriately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20pattern%20I've%20seen%20over%20and%20over%20again%20where%20it's%20after%20the%20fact%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20you%20don't%20start%20monitoring%20impacts%20before%20the%20actual%20new%20form%20of%20gambling%20is%20being%20used%2C%20you%20really%20have%20no%20idea%20what%20the%20baseline%20looked%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20argument%20many%20companies%20will%20make%20is%20that%20people%20will%20gamble%20anyway%20%E2%80%94%20on%20sports%2C%20on%20elections%2C%20on%20whatever%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20making%20it%20legal%20brings%20that%20activity%20into%20the%20light%2C%20gets%20it%20some%20oversight%2C%20and%20generates%20tax%20revenue%20for%20the%20states.%20That's%20true%2C%20but%20also%2C%20once%20the%20government%20greenlights%20it%2C%20people%20who%20otherwise%20wouldn't%20gamble%20start.%20It's%20impossible%20to%20argue%20everyone%20on%20FanDuel%20right%20now%20was%20betting%20on%20sports%20on%20some%20offshore%20account%2010%20years%20ago.%20If%20it%20were%20that%20easy%2C%20sportsbooks%20wouldn't%20be%20investing%20so%20much%20in%20advertising%20to%20draw%20people%20in.%20On%20the%20meme%20coins%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20if%20you%20got%20bamboozled%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fhailey-welch-goes-awol-after-failed-hawk-tuah-token-launch-1034118124%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20%26quot%3BHawk%20Tuah%26quot%3B%20girl's%20crypto%20shenanigans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that's%20at%20least%20a%20little%20bit%20on%20you.%20But%20also%2C%20you%20probably%20deserve%20some%20protection%20next%20time.%20(But%20seriously%2C%20next%20time%2C%20maybe%20think%20that%20one%20over%20a%20bit%20more.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20may%20the%20odds%20be%20ever%20in%20your%20favor%2C%20because%20we're%20not%20getting%20out%20of%20gambling-palooza%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessi