d%20statements%20together%2C%20the%20message%20seems%20to%20be%20this%3A%20The%20ruling%20class%20must%20be%20alert%20to%20contemporary%20issues%20and%20refrain%20from%20focusing%20on%20past%20references.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Priyanka%20highlighted%20the%20ruling%20coalition's%20disconnect%20from%20the%20masses%20in%20her%20maiden%20speech%20in%20Parliament%2C%20let%20us%20apply%20the%20same%20yardstick%20to%20the%20current%20Congress%20leadership.%20They%20must%20adhere%20to%20the%20same%20standards%20they%20set%20for%20others.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20Congress%20secured%20nearly%2014%20crore%20votes%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20governs%20several%20states%2C%20and%20commands%2099%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20The%20Congress%20Really%20'Connected'%20To%20People%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20assume%20for%20a%20moment%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98connected'%20Congress%20leadership%20has%20an%20effective%20mechanism%20in%20place%20to%20gather%20timely%20feedback%20from%20the%20ground.%20If%20that%20is%20the%20case%2C%20then%20why%20have%20they%20suffered%20a%20series%20of%20shocking%20election%20defeats%2C%20even%20in%20states%20where%20they%20seemed%20to%20have%20an%20upper%20hand%3F%20What%20explains%20the%20party's%20stagnation%20in%20terms%20of%20adding%20votes%20over%20the%20past%2015%20years%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20lies%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20current%20Congress%20leadership%20is%20entirely%20disconnected%20from%20the%20reality%20of%20%E2%80%98what%20is'%20and%20overly%20focused%20on%20%E2%80%98what%20ought%20to%20be'.%20Their%20%E2%80%98ought%20to%20be'%20approach%20stems%20from%20a%20sense%20of%20entitlement.%20Since%20previous%20Congress%20governments%20established%20PSUs%20like%20SAIL%2C%20ONGC%2C%20BHEL%2C%20GAIL%2C%20built%20IITs%20and%20IIMs%2C%20created%20AIIMS%2C%20implemented%20economic%20reforms%2C%20and%20followed%20a%20specific%20brand%20of%20secularism%2C%20they%20believe%20they%20are%20entitled%20to%20preach%20to%20the%20people%20about%20what%20should%20happen%2C%20rather%20than%20focusing%20on%20the%20routine%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20else%20can%20we%20explain%20their%20stubborn%20refusal%20to%20course-correct%2C%20their%20continued%20focus%20on%20issues%20like%20the%20caste%20census%20(which%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20I%20support)%2C%20the%20claim%20that%20the%20Constitution%20is%20under%20threat%20(leading%20to%20an%20unnecessary%20four-day%20debate%20in%20Parliament)%2C%20the%20repeated%20narrative%20of%20EVM%20tampering%20in%20the%20face%20of%20electoral%20defeat%2C%20or%20their%20single-minded%20pursuit%20in%20targeting%20business%20houses%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDitch%20The%20Old%20Congress%20Playbook%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20%E2%80%98connected'%20Congress%20leadership%2C%20I%20offer%20some%20recent%20reports%20as%20a%20reality%20check%3A%20Simran%20Shaikh%2C%20a%20girl%20from%20Dharavi%2C%20became%20the%20most%20expensive%20player%20in%20the%20WPL%20(if%20this%20is%20not%20a%20celebration%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20what%20is%3F)%3B%20Jatin%20Kumar%2C%20the%20son%20of%20a%20retired%20Havildar%2C%20won%20the%20prestigious%20Sword%20of%20Honour%20at%20the%20Indian%20Military%20Academy's%20passing-out%20parade%20(yet%20another%20sign%20of%20a%20robust%20Constitution%20at%20work)%3B%20retail%20investors%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20a%20record%20Rs%203%20lakh%20crore%20in%20equity%20capital%20raised%20by%20India%20Inc%20in%202024%20alone%20(does%20this%20not%20show%20that%20people%20are%20not%20aligned%20with%20Congress's%20business%20bashing%3F)%3B%20more%20independent%20members%20are%20joining%20company%20boards%2C%20signalling%20an%20improvement%20in%20corporate%20governance.%20Shouldn't%20the%20%E2%80%98connected'%20Congress%20leadership%20take%20note%20of%20these%20and%20countless%20other%20headlines%20and%20figure%20out%20whether%20the%20issues%20they%20continuously%20raise%20are%20truly%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20people%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi%20has%20demonstrated%20flexibility%2C%20seems%20capable%20of%20giving%20a%20new%20direction%20to%20her%20party%2C%20is%20not%20afraid%20to%20hit%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20comes%20across%20as%20someone%20willing%20to%20abandon%20the%20beaten%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20she%20needs%20to%20do%20is%20leave%20behind%20the%20current%20Congress%20playbook%2C%20which%20has%20long%20expired.%20Focus%20on%20the%20present.%20Be%20honest%20about%20the%20feedback%20from%20the%20ground.%20Stop%20grabbing%20attention%20on%20social%20media%20with%20gimmicks%20(the%20sticker%20on%20her%20bag%20was%20just%20that).%20Stop%20lecturing%20the%20people%20on%20what%20they%20should%20do.%20The%20Congress%20has%20a%20rich%20tradition%20and%20Priyanka%20is%20smart%20enough%20to%20draw%20on%20the%20best%20qualities%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20Narasimha%20Rao%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20Manmohan%20Singh.%20These%20leaders%20did%20what%20they%20believed%20was%20right%20for%20the%20country%20at%20their%20respective%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstand%20The%20Modi%20Era%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20now%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20era.%20To%20mount%20a%20semblance%20of%20a%20challenge%2C%20Priyanka%20must%20first%20understand%20the%20basics%20of%20what%20it%20stands%20for.%20Bold%20welfarism%2C%20a%20thriving%20equity%20culture%2C%20assertive%20nationalism%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20a%20large%2C%20caste-agnostic%20youth%20demographic%2C%20and%20a%20confident%2C%20aspirational%20India%20that%20is%20starting%20to%20dream%20big%E2%80%94these%20are%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20the%20Modi%20era.%20One%20cannot%20dismiss%20them.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20my%20previous%20column%2C%20I%20offered%20some%20food%20for%20thought.%20I%20argued%20that%20the%20Congress%20cannot%20hope%20to%20grow%20as%20long%20as%20it%20ignores%20the%20aspirations%20of%20a%20rising%20India.%20I%20concluded%20with%20a%20fictional%20tale%20in%20which%20the%20protagonist%20is%20left%20with%20many%20regrets%2C%20having%20failed%20to%20accept%20reality.%20Priyanka%20must%20not%20go%20down%20that%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20regarding%20Priyanka's%20claim%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EPaise%20ke%20bal%20par%20sarkar%20giraaye%20jaate%20hain%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E(governments%20are%20dismantled%20with%20money).%20An%20article%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%20%3C%2Fem%3Equotes%20a%20law%20professor%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbetween%201957%20and%201967%2C%20as%20many%20as%2097%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20defected%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20419%20defected%20to%20it%26quot%3B.%20This%20was%2C%20incidentally%2C%20a%20period%20of%20idealism%20in%20Indian%20politics.%20Defections%20driven%20by%20the%20pressures%20of%20money%20and%20muscle%20power%20became%20a%20menace%20subsequently%2C%20leading%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20to%20introduce%20the%20anti-defection%20law%20in%20the%201980s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20urge%20Priyanka%20to%20reconsider%20her%20stance%20in%20light%20of%20these%20historical%20facts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Consulting%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734594240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F76q4eeq8_priyanka-gandhi-_160x120_23_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-priyanka-must-discard-if-shes-serious-about-congress-revival-7283975%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20problem%20lies%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20current%20Congress%20leadership%20is%20entirely%20disconnected%20from%20the%20reality%20of%20what%20is%20and%20overly%20focused%20on%20what%20ought%20to%20be.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%