0for%20cricketers%20but%20in%20general.%20Generally%2C%20when%20I%20go%20to%20sleep%20I%20remember%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20like%20taking%20wickets%2C%20making%20runs%2C%20but%20those%20memories%20are%20not%20there%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20that%20was%20a%20clear%20indication%20that%20we%20need%20to%20take%20a%20different%20route%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20set%20any%20new%20goals%2C%20as%20I%20just%20want%20to%20relax%20now.%20Actually%2C%20it's%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20stay%20inactive%2C%20but%20I%20want%20to%20try%20that%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20continue%20to%20play%20club%20cricket%2C%20including%20the%20IPL%2C%20where%20he%20will%20return%20to%20play%20for%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20part%20for%20me%20is%20still%20burning%20bright.%20I%20am%20going%20to%20play%20for%20CSK%20and%20don't%20be%20surprised%20if%20I%20aspire%20to%20play%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can.%20I%20don't%20think%20Ashwin%20the%20cricketer%20is%20done%2C%20I%20think%20only%20Ashwin%20the%20Indian%20cricketer%20called%20time.%20That's%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20reiterated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20limited-overs%20format%2C%20being%20part%20of%20the%202011%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%202013%20Champions%20Trophy-winning%20teams%20would%20count%20among%20the%20major%20highlights%20of%20his%2014-year%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20played%20116%20ODIs%20for%20India%2C%20claiming%20156%20wickets%2C%20while%20his%2065%20T20%20International%20outings%20yielded%2072%20scalps.%20His%20career%20began%20in%202010%20in%20the%20one-day%20format%20before%20he%20made%20his%20Test%20debut%20a%20year%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C