the%20institution%20is%20giving%20them%20all%20the%20right%20practical%20assignments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Sparkling%20Mindz%2C%20students%20aged%20between%2014%20and%2017%20are%20called%20%E2%80%98Unicorns%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20highest%20level%20in%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20age-based%20hierarchy.%20The%20journey%20starts%20with%20toddlers%20as%20%E2%80%98Guppies%E2%80%99%20and%20progresses%20through%20%E2%80%98Pups%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Calves%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Cubs%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Joeys%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Dolphins%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Leopards%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98Falcons%E2%80%99%2C%20culminating%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98Unicorns%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Unicorns%20pull%20out%20some%20data%20from%20their%20recent%20work%2C%20Sreeja%20explains%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20unusual%20for%20Bengaluru%20to%20face%20such%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296593%2Fbengaluru-floods-zenrainman-s-vishwanath-expert-shares-water-logging-solutions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclimatic%20unpredictabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20problem%20lies%20in%20how%20young%20people%20view%20it%20from%20a%20very%20surface%20level.%20In%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20safeguard%20its%20vulnerable%2C%20they%20are%20just%20given%20a%20holiday%20from%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20in%20that%20act%20of%20protection%2C%20who%20is%20addressing%20their%20reactions%20towards%20these%20calamities%3F%20This%20compelled%20our%20children%20to%20wonder%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296793%2Fex-army-officer-restores-stormwater-drains-bengaluru-rains-floods-water-logging-solution%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhy%20does%20Bengaluru%20flood%20when%20it%20rains%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%20And%20why%20are%20most%20kids%20indifferent%20towards%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%2