20two%20more%20Bandicoot%20robots%20to%20their%20inventory%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20six%20that%20were%20already%20employed.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20gained%20significant%20recognition%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%20attending%20the%20launch%20of%20an%20early%20Bandicoot%20model%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Bandicoot%2C%20Genrobotics%20has%20also%20developed%20other%20robots%20for%20specialised%20tasks%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Wilboar%2C%20designed%20for%20cleaning%20petroleum%20tanks%2C%20and%20the%20G-Gaiter%2C%20a%20gait-training%20robot%20for%20people%20with%20mobility%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734337800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fscaven_11zon-1734087660.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D389376%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20bold%20move%20to%20eliminate%20the%20dangerous%20and%20degrading%20practice%20of%20manual%20scavenging%2C%20a%20startup%20called%20Genrobotics%20has%20introduced%20the%20Bandicoot%20robot%2C%20a%20high-tech%20solution%20that%20removes%20humans%20from%20hazardous%20sanitation%20tasks%2C%20saves%20lives%2C%20and%20helps%20break%20the%20stigma%20surrounding%20this%20essential%20but%20stigmatised%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F389376%2Fgenrobotics-bandicoot-robot-ending-manual-scavenging%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Bamboo%20Boats%20to%20Soy%20Wax%20Candles%3A%204%20Eco-Friendly%20Innovations%20From%20Northeast%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECreativity%20and%20innovation%20play%20a%20major%20role%20in%20solving%20challenges%20and%20improving%20lives%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20a%20simple%2C%20low-technology%20cold%20storage%20unit%20or%20soy%20wax%20candles%20held%20in%20beautiful%20pottery%20jars.%20India%E2%80%99s%20ranking%20in%20the%20Global%20Innovation%20Index%20(GII)%20has%20improved%20consistently%20over%20the%20years%2C%20and%C2%A0in%202024%2C%20it%20ranked%2039th%20out%20of%20133%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20we%20describe%20four%20interesting%20innovative%20ventures%20from%20Northeast%20India%2C%20known%20for%20its%20rich%20biodiversity%20and%20culture.%20They%20range%20from%20the%20simple%20to%20the%20sophisticated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20ventures%20are%20featured%20in%20the%20book%20%E2%80%98People%E2%80%99s%20Festival%20of%20Innovations%20%E2%80%93%202023%E2%80%99.%20The%20festival%20was%20jointly%20organised%20by%20GIAN%20(Grassroots%20Innovations%20Augmentation%20Network)%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20founded%20by%20Prof%20Anil%20Gupta%2C%20and%20C-CAMP%20(Centre%20for%20Cellular%20and%20Molecular%20Platforms).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Scented%20soy%20wax%20candles%20in%20Longpi%20jars%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ancient%20craft%20of%20Longpi%20black%20pottery%20has%20been%20given%20a%20modern%20twist%20by%20the%20Manipur-based%20venture%20%E2%80%98October%20Pumpkin%2C%E2%80%99%20which%20uses%20these%20handcrafted%20jars%20for%20scented%20soy%20wax%20candles.%20Soy%20wax%2C%20a%20renewable%20and%20biodegradable%20plant-based%20product%2C%20stands%20out%20for%20its%20eco-friendly%20properties%2C%20unlike%20paraffin%20wax%2C%20which%20emits%20harmful%20toxins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20venture%20has%20been%20selected%20by%20BITS%20Pilani%20for%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20funding%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98Womenpreneur%20for%20Bharat%202.0%20program%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2