Fvideos%252F887935758613447%252F%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D560%26t%3D0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22314%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESinghara%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20the%20samosa%20is%20referred%20to%2C%20is%20one%20among%20many%20gems%20at%20this%20eatery.%20The%20others%20include%20cutlets%2C%20%3Cem%3Etelebhaja%20%3C%2Fem%3E(fritters)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emughlai%20porota%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20flaky%20pan-fried%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%20%3C%2Fem%3Estuffed%20with%20meats).%20And%20accompanying%20every%20serving%20is%20ketchup%2C%20spicy%20green%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20curd-based%20dip%2C%20and%20mustard%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Munni%20Lal%20Halwai%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Professor%20Pushpesh%20Pant%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20experts%20on%20Indian%20food%2C%20described%20the%20%3Cem%3Esamosa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccrude%20peasant%20dish%E2%80%9D%20once%20%E2%80%94%20he%20was%20referring%20to%20its%20ability%20to%20appease%20society%20at%20large.%20The%20moniker%20is%20attributed%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Esamosa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20no-frills%20recipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Munni%20Lal%20Halwai%20has%20been%20packing%20a%20punch%20in%20their%20%3Cem%3Esamosas%3C%2Fem%3E%20since%20the%201940s%20at%20a%20rate%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20burn%20a%20hole%20in%20your%20pocket.%20And%20adding%20flavour%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295271%2Forigin-of-chole-bhature-in-india-partition-food-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20classic%20is%20%3Cem%3Echole%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(chickpea%20curry)%2C%20onions%20and%20%3Cem%3Epudhina%20%3C%2Fem%3E(mint)%3Cem%3E%20chutney%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Shri%20Bankey%20Bihari%20Samose%20Wale%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Paharganj%2C%20there%20lies%20a%20shop%20that%20has%20been%20doling%20out%20delicious%20%3Cem%3Esamosas%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20over%2060%20years%20now.%20The%20%3Cem%3Esamosas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehere%20hold%20the%20fancy%20of%20Ajay%20Raghav%2C%20a%20recipe%20curator%20who%20is%20always%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20exquisite%20fare%20served%20by%20legendary%20and%20upcoming%20eateries.%20%E2%80%9CHere%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20crispy%20%3Cem%3Esamosa%20%3C%2Fem%3Efilled%20with%20flavoured%20mashed%20potatoes.%20They%20serve%20%3Cem%3Esamosa%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20%3Cem%3Echole%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20the%20taste%20is%20just%20too%20good!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fsamosa-in-delhi-1-1732281135.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shri%20Bankey%20Bihari%20Samose%20Wale%20is%20a%20legendary%20shop%20that%20serves%20Delhi's%20best%20samosas%3B%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fsamosa-in-delhi-1-1732281135.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fsamosa-in-delhi-1-1732281135-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fsamosa-in-delhi-1-1732281135-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fsamosa-in-delhi-1-1732281135-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fsamosa-in-delhi-1-1732281135-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382208%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShri%20Bankey%20Bihari%20Samose%20Wale%20is%20a%20legendary%20shop%20that%20serves%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20best%20%3Cem%3Esamosas%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20Pictures%20source%3A%20(L)%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22ht