0materials%2C%20thereby%20improving%20their%20livelihoods.%20His%20story%20inspires%20other%20farmers%20to%20leverage%20the%20locally%20available%20farm%20produce%2C%20cater%20to%20the%20challenge%20of%20food%20loss%2Fspoilage%2C%20and%20integrate%20innovative%20clean-energy-powered%20livelihood%20technology%20to%20improve%20their%20incomes%20via%20value%20addition%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Divya%20Gaur%2C%20programme%20lead%2C%20Council%20on%20Energy%2C%20Environment%20and%20Water%20(CEEW).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInspiring%20farmers%20to%20embrace%20solar%20drying%20technology%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolar%20dryers%20enable%20farmers%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282854%2Fmaharashtra-family-solar-drying-machine-food-processing-chikoo-increases-sales%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eefficiently%20dry%20perishable%20commodities%20like%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20flowers%2C%20and%20herbs.%20These%20dryers%20ensure%20the%20highest%20quality%20products%20by%20preventing%20dust%2C%20preserving%20colour%20and%20texture%2C%20protecting%20against%20rain%2C%20and%20maintaining%20overall%20product%20quality%2C%20which%20allows%20farmers%20to%20command%20premium%20prices%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20by%20CEEW%20estimates%20that%20India%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20deploy%20as%20many%20as%201.68%20lakh%20solar%20dryers%2C%20impacting%20up%20to%2034%20lakh%20livelihoods.%20States%20like%20Maharashtra%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Gujarat%20have%20the%20highest%20potential%20for%20these%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-4-1733937822.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221